    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. It offers a great balance of quality and value for someone seeking a dependable, attractive vehicle.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
