      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, providing a reliable driving experience. While the exterior paint retains a nice shine, there are a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. All major electronics and climate control systems are fully functional. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for your next rewarding project? This car is in poor condition and ready for a total transformation, making it the perfect affordable canvas for a restoration enthusiast! It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to roll up your sleeves and bring a vehicle back to life exactly the way you want it.",
      "price": 4500.0,
